channelMetadataRenderer.title: VISION
channelMetadataRenderer.description:
Electronica and bass music record label. Est. by Noisia in 2005.

On this channel we upload our weekly VISION Radio podcast, showcasing what excites us in bass music; drum & bass, electronica, beats and whatever forward leaning sounds we can get our hands on.
